import React from "react";
import { FooterContainer, FooterCons, Wrapper, Menu, MenuItem} from "./footer.elements";

const Footer = () => {

    return<>
        <FooterContainer>
            <Wrapper>
                <Menu>
                    <MenuItem>
                        <FooterCons>
                        </FooterCons>
                    </MenuItem>
                    <MenuItem>
                        <FooterCons>
                        </FooterCons>
                    </MenuItem>
                </Menu>
            </Wrapper>
        </FooterContainer>
    </>
}

export default Footer;
